                    '21532', 'Shioyaki', '', 'Shioyaki (シオヤキ) is a member of the Arlong Pirates. He is the Head of Banquets. His name is a pun which means "fish broiled with salt" and in Japan it''s a common method of preparing salmon. Like Kaneshiro, Pisaro and Nuke he was only named in the Data Books. Source: http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Shioyaki', 
