                ) VALUES (
                    '21688', 'Zenny', '', 'Zenny is the old man from Goat Island. He is debt collector who got stuck in an island for 20 years ago full of goats and is suffering from a fatal disease, though he received medicine from Chopper and is seen once again sailing the sea with the goats. http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Zenny', 
