                ) VALUES (
                    '21805', 'Gonbe', '', 'Gonbe is Chimney''s pet cat, although he is quite clearly a rabbit. Gonbe is never seen away from Chimney''s side and goes where ever she goes, often mimicking what Chimney''s actions. And he is never seen without a broad smile. (Source: One Piece Wikia)', 
