                    '22694', 'Gloriosa', '', 'Elder Nyon (ニョン婆様, Nyon Baasama) is one of the former Empresses for the Kuja tribe before Hancock took over. Hancock refers to her as the former-former-former empress Gloriosa (グロリオーサ).', 
