                ) VALUES (
                    '23023', 'Genbou', '', 'Genbou is one of the Shandian warriors that fought to take back Upper Yard from Eneru. He is fat and bald, and wears a chef''s hat. He uses a bazooka which fires rare (in Skypiea) iron cannonballs as his weapon. He loses to Yama in the Survival Game, but later recovers as the war ends. First Appearance: Chapter 249; Episode 163 (Source: One Piece Wiki)', 
