                ) VALUES (
                    '23530', 'Terracotta', '', 'Terracotta is Igaram''s wife, and the Royal Head Chef who appears very late in the Arabasta arc. Terracotta also looks almost identical to Igaram which prompts some characters to accuse her of being Igaram in drag. Zoro has said, "A couple can only look so much alike!" when he first saw her. Her friend is Meidy. She is voiced by Antimere Robinson in the FUNimation dub of the eighth One Piece movie. First Appearance: Chapter 213; Episode 128 (Source: One Piece Wiki)', 
