                ) VALUES (
                    '23534', 'Farafra', '', 'Farafra is a member of the Rebel army led by Kohza along with Erik. He has hippo teeth. He lost his right hand and right shoulder while protecting Kohza during an enemy attack. First Appearance: Chapter 167; Episode 104 (Source: One Piece Wikia)', 
