                ) VALUES (
                    '59271', 'Odama', '', 'Odama (大玉) is Kodama''s grandfather. He lives in Fireworks Island. He wears kabuki make-up and has a rude attitude, though he still felt sad for the lost of Kodama''s parents. At first, Odama refused to allow her grand-daughter to release the Ball 205 due to its destructive capabilities, but, thanks to Usopp, he decides to release it, making Kodama''s dream come true. First Appearance: Episode 134 Source: http://onepiece.wikia.com/wiki/Odama', 
